
1) In main, the default "okay:0" string is intentionally hard-wired to avoid
   breaking scripts that make use of xmessage's -print option. Please do not
   change or gettextize this string.

2) To quit the program, call prog_cleanup rather than exit. prog_cleanup
   correctly exits with the current value of gx.exit_code.


